Very nice 3 Bedroom, 1.5 bath home in quiet Redford neighborhood.  This bungalow has a finished basement with a half bath and plenty of room to entertain.   Backyard surrounded by privacy fence.
Furnace is prepped for A/C, Newer Electrical Panel (3-yrs) Washer and Dryer are not included in sale.
